mixin architecture()
  section.architecture
    .container
        .architecture__bg-wave
            +icon("icon-bg-intro-wave", "736", "353", true)
        .architecture__bg-wave-mobile
            +icon("icon-bg-intro-wave", "382", "206", true)
        ul.architecture__breadcrumb
            li.architecture__item
                a(href="#index.html").architecture__link Home 
                .architecture__next
                    include ../../../img/svg/arrow-breadcrumbs.svg
            li.architecture__item
                a(href="#blog.html").architecture__link Blog 
                .architecture__next
                    include ../../../img/svg/arrow-breadcrumbs.svg
            li.architecture__item.architecture__item--last
                span(href="#").architecture__link.current Bringing Designs to Life: How VR is Changing Architecture
        .architecture__wrapper
            .architecture__text
                span.architecture__intro VR Architecture
                h2.architecture__title Bringing Designs to Life: How VR is Changing Architecture
                span.architecture__date NASYIYA ULFA | 
                    time(datetime="2022-11-25") 25 NOV 2022
                .architecture__img
                    +img("content", "blog-man", "jpg", 789, 528, "Man in VR headsets")
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--1
                    p Architecture is an art and science that is constantly evolving with technology. 
                        | The industry has gone through various transformations over the years, from pencil 
                        | and paper sketches to computer-aided design (CAD) software. However, one technology 
                        | that is revolutionizing architecture is virtual reality (VR) design.
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--2
                    p With VR design, architects can bring their designs to life and offer clients an immersive 
                        | experience that was previously impossible. The technology enables architects to create a 
                        | virtual representation of their designs, allowing clients to step into the building and 
                        | explore its features and spaces before it is built.
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--3
                    p VR design is a game-changer for architects and clients alike. It enables architects to 
                        | design with a greater level of detail and precision, allowing them to identify 
                        | design flaws and make necessary modifications before construction begins. 
                        | This not only saves time and money but also ensures that the final product 
                        | meets the client's expectations.
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--4
                    p Clients can also benefit from VR design by having a better understanding of 
                        | the design and how it will look and feel in real life. It allows them 
                        | to experience the design in a more realistic way, helping them make informed 
                        | decisions and providing valuable feedback to the architects.
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--5
                    p Moreover, VR design is not only limited to the design phase. It can also be 
                        | used in the construction process to visualize the project's progress and 
                        | identify any issues that may arise.
                .architecture__wrapper-img 
                    +img("content", "blog-1", "jpg", 377, 252, "VR headsets 1")
                    +img("content", "blog-2", "jpg", 377, 252, "VR headsets 2")
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--6
                    p The benefits of VR design in architecture are clear, and the technology 
                        | is becoming increasingly accessible and affordable. More and more 
                        | architects and firms are incorporating VR design into their workflows, 
                        | and the industry is poised for a major transformation.
                .architecture__description.architecture__description--7
                    p In conclusion, VR design is changing the way architects design and bring their 
                        | projects to life. It is a powerful tool that offers a range of benefits, 
                        | from increased precision and efficiency in the design phase to better 
                        | communication and understanding with clients. As the technology becomes 
                        | more advanced and widespread, we can expect to see more innovative designs 
                        | and better-designed buildings in the future.
                span.architecture__mini-title Post Tags :
                .architecture__tags 
                    p #VRDesign #ArchitectureInnovation #VirtualRealityArchitecture 
                        | #BringingDesignsToLife #DesignVisualization #ArchitecturalVisualization 
                        | #RevolutionizingArchitecture #BuildingInVR #DesignThinking #VRInArchitecture
                span.architecture__mini-title.architecture__mini-title--second Share :
                ul.architecture__list-contacts
                    li.architecture__item-contacts.architecture__item-contacts--tw
                        a(href="#" target="_blank", rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer")
                            +icon("icon-twitter", "18", "15")
                    li.architecture__item-contacts.architecture__item-contacts--fc
                        a(href="#" target="_blank", rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer")
                            +icon("icon-facebook", "10", "20")
                    li.architecture__item-contacts.architecture__item-contacts--inst
                        a(href="#" target="_blank", rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer")
                            +icon("icon-instagram", "22", "22")
            .architecture__article
                h4.architecture__title-article Recent Article
                ul.architecture__list-article 
                    li.architecture__item-article 
                        +img("content", "article-1", "jpg", 102, 65, "VR Education")
                        .architecture__text-article 
                            span VR Education
                            .architecture__descript 
                                p The Future of Education: How VR is Revolutionizing the Classroom
                    li.architecture__item-article 
                        +img("content", "article-2", "jpg", 102, 65, "VR Education")
                        .architecture__text-article 
                            span VR Architecture
                            .architecture__descript 
                                p Bringing Designs to Life: How VR is Changing Architecture
                    li.architecture__item-article 
                        +img("content", "article-3", "jpg", 102, 65, "VR Education")
                        .architecture__text-article 
                            span VR Entertainment 
                            .architecture__descript 
                                p Making Events Memorable: The Power of VR for Corporate and Special...
                    li.architecture__item-article.architecture__item-article--last 
                        +img("content", "article-4", "jpg", 102, 65, "VR Education")
                        .architecture__text-article 
                            span VR Event
                            .architecture__descript 
                                p Exploring New Worlds: The Benefits of VR Travel
